title: Matt Damon Acts Out His Entire Film Career in 8 Minutes - Watch Now!
text: Matt Damon carries his clothes into his appearance at The Late Late Show with James Corden on Tuesday evening (September 29) in Los Angeles. The 44-year-old actor recreated his entire twenty year film career in eight minutes by acting out every movie in an abridged version! PHOTOS: Check out the latest pics of Matt Damon [...] Â»
